{"tid":1479253,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(鍵戰/毒撚回合)台灣WEBTOON三毛 : 「那位獨眼龍是收了四千萬安家費，羨慕吧？」","createTime":"2019-08-16T22:39:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T02:09:47.000Z","uid":6097,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f5463f4c1082e737b3ac409725bdf11a51359779","tid":1479253,"uid":6097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T22:39:38.000Z","msg":"我連睇個韓國翻譯漫畫都有三毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌！(依個係好多好多台灣人睇嘅漫畫app: webtoon)<br />\n<br />\n事源係依個留言(熱門TOP 1)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BV5tUwG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBV5tUwG.png&h=0b4d2fb7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n驚悚漫畫 講個女主角用搖控控制身邊人，最後付上沉重代價。<br />\n<br />\n之後我就係無諗過連webtoon都有三毛<br />\n因為大部分讀者都係台灣人<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sLx4sSP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsLx4sSP.png&h=20687d72&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uybpsSQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuybpsSQ.png&h=8ee80796&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8BWpsSR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8BWpsSR.png&h=9a1e9447&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8d2W3rc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8d2W3rc.png&h=d4844380&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我直覺覺得Winnie係臭閪新移民<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">仲要老屈女義士收咗四千萬去整盲自己！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n因為依集漫畫係夜晚十一點之後upload<br />\n真正嘅港台中混戰估計今日先開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依個係同台灣人直接對話嘅好機會<br />\n如果有睇開webtoon請去幫一幫手<br />\n<br />\n無睇想幫手 <br />\n可以dl<a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/hk/app/line-webtoon-%E6%AF%8F%E6%97%A5%E6%BC%AB%E7%95%AB/id894546091\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.apple.com%2Fhk%2Fapp%2Fline-webtoon-%25E6%25AF%258F%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%25BC%25AB%25E7%2595%25AB%2Fid894546091&d=u3dPEc69Okhs1BcqxCk75dqeVONt7zbw7GHn8%2FjWPdo%3D&h=fd5e9aec\" target=\"_blank\">https://apps.apple.com/hk/app/line-webtoon-%E6%AF%8F%E6%97%A5%E6%BC%AB%E7%95%AB/id894546091</a><br />\n搵<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/niMAzGx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FniMAzGx.png&h=7b243752&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最新嗰集嘅留言<br />\n<br />\n然後撳檢舉<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HXH0LOD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHXH0LOD.png&h=3f35dce0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一定唔可以畀班三毛對住台灣人咁樣抹黑我哋女義士</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日唔去紅土嘅你<br />\n希望你可以喺依啲位上幫小小忙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4257ac6041a8f0fb65c0f302f75ffacc64f62333","tid":1479253,"uid":6097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T22:40:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf009dc40b28405ca8da1ea4e94e7ca06c6dcf35","tid":1479253,"uid":6097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T22:40:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a76a3d15726b11f71010b07bfac64dfe15f3d3d1","tid":1479253,"uid":6097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T22:41:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ced8a59e345776b5b96a6e2bdbb6936d2e84217a","tid":1479253,"uid":6097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T22:41:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2746fec22e0091486e455217917c38e7f90c98ad","tid":1479253,"uid":6097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T22:42:52.000Z","msg":"Webtoon真係好多台灣人睇咖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n除咗反抹黑之外<br />\n都係向台灣人文宣香港嘅好機會<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54726970b698ebd7fd3c68dc0f338aedbd3de287","tid":1479253,"uid":244230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T23:17:50.000Z","msg":"Link please <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"695afeb94b6c742da9dc40d2cb98be65948a80da","tid":1479253,"uid":19437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T23:35:08.000Z","msg":"駛唔駛大家籌錢射盲你？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02c49ac6eeffbf7e02bd3acca37cfa2e966066be","tid":1479253,"uid":215715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T02:09:47.000Z","msg":"5000萬-4000萬<br />\n屌你689食夾棍食成千萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}